#, fuzzy
msgid "https://pt.quarkus.io/guides/smallrye-graphql-client[quarkus-smallrye-graphql-client]"
msgstr "https://pt.quarkus.io/guides/smallrye-graphql-client[quarkus-smallrye-graphql-client]"

#. type: Plain text
